		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I use EKROM beacause it's 100% compatible both with ETROM and EWROM (so the game can run or any ETROM or EWROM devcard).
<br />But, if I need more SRAM, I'll certainly it on ETROM or EWROM (but EWROM is often badly emulated beacause of 32kb SRAM).

		

